sedang mengajari Dewi berlatih.

491
00:32:25,240 --> 00:32:26,160
Jiang Mengmeng.

492
00:32:26,800 --> 00:32:28,120
Aku sebenarnya membantumu…

493
00:32:29,040 --> 00:32:30,160
